description:
&rdquo;Is it okay to kill people?&quot;
A treacherous revenge suspense by Shiryu Nakatake, a newcomer to Bessatsu Shonen Magazine.

&quot;Shun, if someone is converted, let him go and do nothing. He should be given a chance to be reborn.&quot;

&quot;Grandpa, I hope he doesn't reincarnate himself.&quot;
In order to defeat several non-human monsters, the boy also became something non-human.

Shun Uruma, a sixth-grade student, was named &quot;Experimental body: A&quot; by five of his classmates and was severely bullied and lived in hell. His only peace was with his brother, who loved him, and his parents, who protected him.... . until the five monsters killed his family.

When he finally loses everything and faces true hell, a dark &quot;wish&quot; is born inside Shun. He was reborn under the training of his grandfather, who served in a secret unit during WWII. Now, four years later, he appears in front of his fated enemy.

&quot;I won't let ANYONE get in the way of my revenge.&quot;

[b][u]French / Fran&ccedil;ais[/u][/b]
[spoiler]&quot;Est-ce que c'est bien de tuer des gens ?&quot;

Un thriller de vengeance par Shiryu Nakatake, un nouveau venu dans le magazine Bessatsu Shōnen.

Shun Uruma, un &eacute;l&egrave;ve de 6&egrave;me, a &eacute;t&eacute; nomm&eacute; &quot;Sujet de test A&quot; par cinq de ses camarades de classe. Il a &eacute;t&eacute; s&eacute;v&egrave;rement malmen&eacute; et a v&eacute;cu un enfer. Sa seule joie &eacute;tait son fr&egrave;re, qui l'aimait, et ses parents, qui le prot&eacute;geaient... jusqu'&agrave; ce que ces cinq monstres tuent sa famille.
Lorsqu'il perd finalement tout et qu'il affronte le v&eacute;ritable enfer, un sombre &quot;souhait&quot; na&icirc;t en lui. Il rena&icirc;t sous l'entra&icirc;nement de son grand-p&egrave;re, qui a servi dans une unit&eacute; secr&egrave;te pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale. Aujourd'hui, quatre ans plus tard, il appara&icirc;t devant son ennemi jur&eacute;.

&quot;Je ne laisserai personne m'enlever cette vengeance.&quot;[/spoiler]
